# NEWS

## v0.0.0 (20 Feb 2018)
 * Package release

## v0.0.1 (21 Feb 2018)
 * Add examples section in `climdexGrid`
 * Add README file
 * Other minor changes in on-screen messages

## v0.1.0 (23 Feb 2018)
 * Support for multimember grids
 * Replaced parallelization along space by members
 * Other minor changes in on-screen messages

## v0.1.1 (2 Mar 2018)
 * Bug fix in the retrieval of metadata for ensemble members

## v0.1.2 (2 Mar 2018)
 * Minor bug fix to include dimensional consistency check for input grids of multivariable index GSL

## v0.1.3 (9 May 2018)
 * Fix a missing import for `transformeR::bindGrid.member`

## v0.1.4 (15 Aug 2018)
* Replace calls to `bindGrid.*` internals by `bindGrid` with appropriate arguments

## v0.2.0 (18 Dec 2018)
* Support for station data, with an example
* Doc update and a few typos fixed

## v0.2.1 (16 Apr 2019)
* Minor change in the climdexShow display